name: JSP Multiplayer
description:
Before it was only you in the city. But now! Now you can jump around with your friends! This the normal mode fom the original just some parkour, just with local-multiplayer

Instructions is in game

Note: This a Lan game, wich means that you need to be on the same internet to play together

Note 2: This game can see your IP, this is only used to say wich IP you should connect to

Note 3: This is not a triple A game, expect bugs. 

HAVE FUN!
